data.description: Welcome to a residence of distinction in West Mayfair, boasting over 3000 square feet of  living space. This property, a blend of modern amenities and classic charm, offers a rare opportunity in a coveted neighborhood. Upon entering, you are greeted by a generously sized living room, bathed in natural light, featuring a striking brick fireplace - an inviting space for relaxation and social gatherings. The journey through the home reveals a formal dining area with a large pantry/closet, leading to an expansive, well-appointed eat-in kitchen. This culinary space flows into a delightful four-season room, equipped with electric heating and panoramic sliding glass doors, opening to an impressive backyard ideal for summer entertainment and leisure. Upstairs, the master suite presents a private sanctuary with an en-suite bath, complemented by three additional spacious bedrooms with sizable closets and a well-designed full bathroom with double sinks. The basement, along with the crawlspace under the entire area of the kitchen, provides ample storage . Other features include both new plumbing pipes and electrical rewiring throughout, newer water heater, a newer front cement porch, a paver side patio and a generous driveway that accommodates 2-3 vehicles. Situated conveniently near Pennypack Park, major routes and public transport, this home represents a perfect balance of elegance and practicality. We invite you to schedule a viewing and envision your future in this remarkable home.
